  "name": "stellar-private-payments",
  "description": "A proof-of-concept privacy-preserving payment system for the Stellar network, enabling private deposits, transfers, and withdrawals via Groth16 zero-knowledge proofs (Circom circuits) running in the browser through WebAssembly, with Soroban smart contracts enforcing Association Set Provider (ASP) membership and non-membership controls. Note: this project has over 100 source files; consider scoping analysis to a subdirectory for faster results.",
